        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "命名确实一样，但作用域不同，一个是租户实例，一个是库里的基类，这样设计是故意的。另外library里还需要两个IngressController，一个叫D一个叫E吧，分别对应不同的实现。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "library",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把结构搭出来：tenant子图里有A节点Infra_WorkerNode和B节点Infra_LoadBalancer，library子图里有C节点Infra_LoadBalancer、D和E两个Infra_IngressController。方向用从左到右。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
