      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "继承关系要画清楚：WorkerNode A继承自library里的LoadBalancer C，租户环境的LoadBalancer B继承自IngressController D。注意B不是继承C，这是很多人搞错的地方。",
